Tk::FontDialog Module

Tk::FontDialog is a font chooser for perl/Tk. Version 800 of Tk is
required.

To install, type

	$ perl Makefile.PL
	$ make
	$ make install

"make test" starts a test window and serves as an example script,
since there is no pod yet.

Send bug reports, comments and suggestions to eserte@cs.tu-berlin.de
